verbose_text: The small-molecule inhibitor INCA-6 and the peptide inhibitor 11R-VIVIT (VIVIT) act selectively to prevent the association of calcineurin with substrates that bind via the calcineurin PxIxIT docking motif.
evidence: INCA-6               and the peptide inhibitor 11R-VIVIT (VIVIT)               act selectively to prevent the association of calcineurin
